{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"LTR（从左到右）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ltr","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>LTR</strong>（<strong>从左到右</strong>，Left To Right）是<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Locale\">区域设置 <small>(en-US)</small></a>的属性之一，用于指示语言从左到右的书写方向。例如，使用美式英语的 <code>en-US</code> 区域就是从左到右的书写方向。</p>\n<p>大多数西方语言，如同世界上的其他语言一样，都是从左向右书写的。</p>\n<p>与 LTR 相对的是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/rtl\">RTL</a>（从右到左，Right To Left），在另一些语言中常用，例如阿拉伯语（<code>ar</code>）和希伯来语（<code>he</code>）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary\">MDN Web 文档术语</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Locale\">locale <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Localization\">本地化</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ltr\" aria-current=\"page\">LTR（从左到右）</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/rtl\">RTL（从右到左）</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">HTML 全局属性</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-dir\"><code>dir</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-lang\"><code>lang</code></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/:dir\"><code>:dir</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction\"><code>direction</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode\"><code>writing-mode</code></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"LTR（从左到右，Left To Right）是区域设置 (en-US)的属性之一，用于指示语言从左到右的书写方向。例如，使用美式英语的 en-US 区域就是从左到右的书写方向。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"LTR (Left To Right)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ltr","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"LTR (左書き)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/ltr","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/ltr/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ltr","title":"LTR（从左到右）"}],"pageTitle":"LTR（从左到右） - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}